Browser Events

WebSockets

Local Storage

Document Title
```

These are called

```
Side Effects
```

---

# What is a Side Effect?

A Side Effect is anything that affects something outside the React component.

Examples

✅ Fetching users

✅ Saving data

✅ Starting a timer

✅ Reading Local Storage

✅ Changing page title

---

Not Side Effects

```
Rendering JSX

Calculating 10+20

Displaying Variables
```

These stay inside React.

---

